{"_path":"/trail/t012","_dir":"trail","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"大峽谷/八里 水牛坑","description":null,"image":null,"sequence":12,"category":"林口","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口 - 社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"健康休閒"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-03-30T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"大峽谷八里-水牛坑"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"大峽谷/八里 水牛坑"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"步道簡介"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"步道簡介"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"據報導，這裡原本只是一處小山丘，因人為非法開採砂石，造成部分山丘被挖掉大半而形成這狀似「美國大峽谷」的地貌，因此後來被人稱做「林口大峽谷」，而水牛坑的由來，是因為起初當地人家在此放養水牛，後來越繁殖越多，水牛成群，最多時期可以看到 2-300 頭水牛成群吃草的壯觀景象，因而才有「水牛坑」之稱!"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這裡的 山丘為粗粒沙岩、頁岩、泥岩所組成的大南灣層，可說是大台北地區研究地質最好的天然教室，來此體驗一片荒漠景象，不由得讓人憶起美國西部牛仔~那荒野大鏢客的電影情節場景"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"自行開車"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自行開車"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"林口台 15 線西部濱公路 18.3K 公路旁。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"停車：當地可以找到停車位"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"公共運輸"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公共運輸"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"搭乘 F236(新北市林口免費公)至”林投站“下車走 2~3 分鐘。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"相關介紹"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相關介紹"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"健行筆記 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://hiking.biji.co/index.php?q=news&act=info&id=9628"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"林口大峽谷/八里水